public class ClaimAbstractView
extends com.guidewire.pl.persistence.code.BeanBase
implements KeyableBean
    ClaimAbstractView Supports the efficient creation of claim lists in ClaimCenter's views. The system uses this entity to list claims in the desktop, search, and team view in an optimum manner. This is a virtual entity and is not stored in the database.
